<!--
  PROFILE CUSTOM TABS SNIPPET

  Adds the "Inklings" tab to the character profile page tab list.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs

  INSTALLATION:

  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs
  2. Copy the code block below this comment:
     - If the file is empty or nearly empty, paste it as-is
     - If the file already has other tabs, add it after the closing </li> of
       another tab entry (maintain the existing indentation and structure)

  IMPORTANT:
  - DO NOT change the href="#inklings-tab-pane" - it must match the
    id="inklings-tab-pane" in profile-custom.snippet.hbs
  - The Inklings web components (inklings-tab.js, inkling-detail-modal.js,
    inkling-create-form.js, inklings-search.js) are automatically installed
    via the plugin installer - no manual file copying needed.
  - The web portal integration is entirely optional.
-->

<li class="nav-item">
  <a class="nav-link" data-bs-toggle="tab" href="#inklings-tab-pane">Inklings</a>
</li>
